OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Norrie
OL,4,CBartlett
OL,6,FNorrie Bartlett, Age 98, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 7 March 2024
OL,10,FOffshore from Gold Beach on D-Day on a
OL,11,Fwarship, Mr Bartlett from Surrey was
OL,12,Finside a turret firing a 4.5 inch
OL,13,Fnaval gun to protect those who were
OL,14,Flanding.
OL,16,FEarlier his ship had helped escort
OL,17,Fother vessels crossing the Channel.
OL,19,F"The shells used to come up
OL,20,Fautomatically," he said.
