OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Norrie
OL,4,CBartlett
OL,6,F"From down below where they had been
OL,7,Ffused ready for exploding. They loaded
OL,8,Finto the turret and also we put them
OL,9,Fin a barrel and when we were ordered
OL,10,Ffired them.
OL,12,F"When (the troops) started to land,
OL,13,Fthat's when we began to bombard the
OL,14,FGerman defences - horrendous.
OL,16,F"Bearing in mind the battleships were
OL,17,Fsix or seven miles offshore - some of
OL,18,Fthe troops were firing anyway.
