OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Norrie
OL,4,CBartlett
OL,6,F"I am concentrating on where my gun is
OL,7,Faiming, and we weren't hit at all
OL,8,Fbecause they were concentrating on the
OL,9,Ftroops going on the beach.
OL,11,F"We left when all the troops had
OL,12,Flanded.
OL,14,F"We were sent back to Portsmouth and
OL,15,Fhad to escort more merchant ships
OL,16,Fwhich were carrying spares and guns.
OL,18,F"We escorted them back down to the
OL,19,Fbeaches again, and stayed there that
OL,20,Fnight - then we went back to
OL,21,FPortsmouth again.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
