OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Norrie
OL,4,CBartlett
OL,6,F"We just thought we were doing a job
OL,7,Fand we did it the best we could. There
OL,8,Fwas no heroics about it.
OL,10,F"I will be quite honest we were all
OL,11,Fdead scared, I don't mind admitting
OL,12,Fit. We had two chances. Get away with
OL,13,Fit or go under."
OL,15,FMr Bartlett had originally trained as
OL,16,Fa gunner at the Royal Navy's Whale
OL,17,FIsland training base in Portsmouth.
OL,19,FPrior to the landings his ship had
OL,20,Fbeen in the Dover Straits firing at
OL,21,Fpositions in the Calais region.
